Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.07,0:00:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神Zwei
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.39,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.61,0:00:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.44,0:00:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.82,0:01:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.36,0:01:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.70,0:01:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「粉碎的女神(機組)」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.45,0:02:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生...請問要用餐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐身上\N沒有出現任何異常情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意識無法恢復的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.47,0:02:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是來自於精神上的打擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐她現在\N正拒絕接受現實的世界...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個狀況要是繼續下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論莉露還是其他人都會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說都是斗牙的錯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...那小子太搞不清楚狀況了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.57,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不懂自己不經意所做的事\N到底會給對方帶來多大的影響...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙也是以他的方式\N在關心著莉露呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他並不是有意的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才更饒不了他嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他總是那樣一直笑著\N也想要當個乖寶寶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事情完全不是那麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那小子...\N他不知道什麼叫痛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了...夠了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為從來都沒有人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教他到底什麼才叫做痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起戰鬥的方式...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該有更優先\N教會的事情才對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...\N他已經一點一點的在改變了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在英司你來了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在莉露加入了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連斗牙自己都說\N他想要改變了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情為什麼會變成這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他想自己一個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露要是看到這些花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會不會高興呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.09,0:04:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都這麼不加思索的\N做了很傷人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到被英司這麼罵了之後\N我才真的注意到這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就只會一直傷害大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻什麼...什麼都不能挽回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺原來您在這裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到斗牙少爺了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安撫斗牙少爺這件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光憑我實在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這或許是我的錯也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為我一直都伺候在他身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺才會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這樣的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺能這麼順利的\N成長到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這全都是靠愛娜的愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自個兒硬鑽牛角尖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是連妳都開始心煩的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是反而讓斗牙少爺\N感到更痛苦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是媚月小姐能在的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種企圖在廢棄水霸上著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因為干擾力場展開的影響\N無法掌握目前狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.48,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影與G打擊機的\N幽靈系統搭載作業已經完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.42,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須有兩部用幽靈出擊啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎們遭受打擊的情形\N似乎也很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的能夠作戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全機出發準備完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G打擊機 G攻擊機\N出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影\NG鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現場的情形還不明朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.48,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外星異種分析結果出來前\N不要勉強進行攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20秒後將會到達現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.07,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼隨便就打了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.34,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點合神啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有兩架是用幽靈系統不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神後的神機超重神出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.49,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有平時的61.9%...\N這樣風險相當大!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神...不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先觀察一下情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交由各機判斷各自進行攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干擾力場消失!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一大堆什麼東西耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求照准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位\N啟動合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這種手段...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太齷齪了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然是\N瞄準了合神的那一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁機封印住超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種...開始侵蝕超重皇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種...開始吸取\N超重皇的重力子能源了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去\N駕駛員會無法承受負荷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗...斗牙少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西!\N打算把超重皇生吞活剝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們左右包抄牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把外星異種從斗牙身上剝下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃彈頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快照我的意思去動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法\N這樣子根本無法靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...再這樣下去的話斗牙就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜! 愛娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊...超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把我...殺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去的話\N超重皇會繼續失控的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把地球變的和蘭比亞斯一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有駕駛員\N超重皇應該就會停止行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣因為我的關係\N而傷害到大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在鬼扯什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我振作點斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把你救出來的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.35,0:14:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有辦法...保護別人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不用再勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們快動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙我現在就趕過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實現和你的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜...妳要做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.08,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種正從超重皇內\N吸取重力子能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要直接與其接觸\N並讓被抽取出來的能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.39,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入G鑽機的重力子循環系統\N並在增幅後反饋回去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.77,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能救出斗牙少爺了\N也說不定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情...有可能辦到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是讓我去的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是桑德曼先生\N創造出來的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"原型.超重機組"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"原型.超重機組"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜開始轉換為\N原初.超重機組模式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快切斷轉換!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.06,0:15:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有效!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部超重機組都無法控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有機能都被愛娜遮蔽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G鑽機在執行分離程序?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事?無法操作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛...愛娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺他...就麻煩您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜妳想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.43,0:16:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋為什麼動不了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司快阻止她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜她想要犧牲自己!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜不要這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳快點回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了斗牙少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您要活下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是...真的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡! 那混蛋居然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.38,0:18:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體還...可惡\N為什麼都沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點動快點動啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙快逃啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重鑽機...左側駕駛艙\N反應消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員...沒有回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣?連琉菜小姐也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...我不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊陣列V
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電光雷管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JACKOFF(回家吃自己吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA的量產型超重神...\N已經完成了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.08,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是...妳所追求的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是超重要塞\N開始回收超重皇與G攻擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫療班請立即待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武裝女僕班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在現場散開後開始搜救G鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請以這項任務為第一優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是...我們的力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.74,0:21:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然就只有這點斤兩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼和計算中的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人期待的是以後的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重...皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱旋歸建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是空的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.55,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.93,0:22:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.54,0:22:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.41,0:22:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.88,0:22:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.36,0:22:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.96,0:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.47,0:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.44,0:23:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.98,0:23:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.65,0:23:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.59,0:23:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.94,0:23:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了啦\N再哭愛娜也一樣回不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞孃、布麗姬妲、雪希爾\N妳們振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要連愛娜的份\N一起努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.55,0:23:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.21,0:23:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.32,0:23:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不見了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.72,0:23:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回\N「在重力衰弱的時刻」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.42,0:23:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回我們也要照料各位的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜姊...